Hetuduka, Tika
Hetuduka, Saṃkiliṭṭhattika
Saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikapada
Pañhāvāra
Paccayacatukka
Hetvādi
190.
349Hetu saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko dhammo hetussa saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo…  tīṇi.
350Hetu saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko dhammo hetussa saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo…  nava.
351Hetu saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko dhammo hetussa saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesikassa dhammassa adhipatipaccayena paccayo—  ārammaṇādhipati…  nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
191.
352Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava, anantare nava, samanantare nava, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe nava, nissaye nava, upanissaye nava, āsevane nava, kamme tīṇi, āhāre tīṇi, indriye tīṇi, jhāne tīṇi, magge tīṇi, sampayutte nava, atthiyā nava, natthiyā nava, vigate nava, avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
